OL,7,FShe was handed a 15-month prison
OL,8,Fsentence on her son's 10th birthday in
OL,9,FNovember 2010 and was eight weeks'
OL,10,Fpregnant when jailed.
OL,12,FMrs Misra's conviction was quashed by
OL,13,Fthe Court of Appeal in 2021.
OL,15,FFollowing her conviction and sentence,
OL,16,FMr Smith sent an email to managers,
OL,17,Fincluding Paula Vennells, asking to
OL,18,F"pass on my thanks" to the legal team.
