OL,7,F"However, knowing what I do now, it is
OL,8,Fevident that my email would have
OL,9,Fcaused Seema Misra and her family
OL,10,Fsubstantial distress to read, and I
OL,11,Fwould like to apologise for that.
OL,13,F"My comment of 'brilliant news' was in
OL,14,Frelation to me thinking that it was
OL,15,Fbrilliant news that, in my mind,
OL,16,FHorizon had been proved to be robust
OL,17,Ffollowing the testing of the expert
OL,18,Fevidence in the trial.
